Constructor Detail

CSysTableAdapterForResultSet

public CSysTableAdapterForResultSet()
Constructs an new CSysResultTable and fills it with the data from the given ResultSet. All the names and datatype informations from the ResultSet are used to create the columns in the CSysResultTable.
Traditionally unsupported types:
NULL
OTHER

And all new types (See Also: What Is in the JDBC 2.0 API since: 1.2)
JAVA_OBJECT
DISTINCT
STRUCT
ARRAY
BLOB
CLOB
REF
